Air Berlin Hires Consultant to Find New CEO, Manager Mag Reports

-- B y   R a j i v   S e k h r i
-- 
2011-09-21T08:19:17Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-21/air-berlin-hires-consultant-to-find-new-ceo-manager-mag-reports.html
Air Berlin Plc (AB1)  has hired personnel
consultancy Egon Zehnder to search for a new chief executive to
replace Hartmut Mehdorn soon, Manager Magazin reported today,
without saying how it obtained the information.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Rajiv Sekhri at 
 rsekhri1@bloomberg.net  